::Kaiser::
       He shouts after Rodimus.  "We shall meet again Rodimus Prime.  And I 
am looking forward to it.  I think I would enjoy our battle.  Until then."  
He stands between the retreating Rodimus and the rest of the battle.  He lays 
down a covering fire pattern across the battle to distract them during the 
escape.
